Text:
She is amazing! I am a die hard fan, and I would give up anything to have one night with her...if ya know what i mean..and im as straight as an arrow, except for her. Her voice is amazing. I think love game is good, but one of her lowest grade songs when it comes to talent. Every time I hear her sing acoustic my heart melts and i fall in love....
